metadata.Plot: On a boring winter afternoon, Alice dreams, that she's visiting the land behind the mirror. This turns out to be a surrealistic nightmare, with all sorts of strange things happening to her, like changing her size or playing croquet with flamingos.
metadata.Director: Norman Z. McLeod, Hugh Harman, Rudolf Ising
metadata.Writer: Joseph L. Mankiewicz, William Cameron Menzies, Lewis Carroll
metadata.Actors: Richard Arlen, Roscoe Ates, William Austin
